                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "《原神》2.4版本PV：「飞彩镌流年」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/15/142453215/feab5d3627cfa529fc15798565055b7d_2580170926795710714.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2021年12月26日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "华彩难及之处，诡谲的敌影伺机而动。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "白昼永无之境，残存的火种仍未平息。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "而在日光照耀的地方，人们依然满怀期待。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "那些诚挚的希望，一如盛放的烟火，流光溢彩。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "《原神》2.5版本PV：「薄樱初绽时」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/15/142453215/f2db459e7cac76c8ee70779ec37e82c6_8366422823113481613.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年2月4日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "神樱自古立于影向山顶，根系深盘地底，绵延不绝。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "在它的荫蔽之下，有人类诚心祈福，有妖狐笑看浮世，也有神明梦系须臾永恒。世事流转，人聚又散，唯有绯樱连年烂漫，随风而安。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "音乐",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "《原神》佚落迁忘之岛 Islands of the Lost and Forgotten",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/15/142453215/b2e208bb00ad10ab3b14599e3ccf812a_1691287909434657718.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年4月13日",
                      "type": "text"
